    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec E46 M3 powered by the iconic S54B32 inline-six. This unit features a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. The high-revving valvetrain is in excellent health, with the double-VANOS system functioning within factory tolerances. The chassis remains rigid, having undergone a preventative subframe reinforcement and a recent suspension refresh with OEM bushings to maintain its razor-sharp handling characteristics. While the paint displays minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals are top-tier, featuring a cooling system overhaul and consistent oil analysis. A mechanically honest example for the discerning purist.",
