    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver that still turns heads. The exterior paint retains a deep luster, showing only minor, age-appropriate stone chips that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership: the upholstery is free of tears, the dashboard is crack-free, and all electronic features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, backed by a consistent service history. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection, ensuring it is road-ready. The tires have excellent tread depth, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a solid, honest car for someone who values mechanical integrity and a clean aesthetic.",
